-- Petrofac Wins U.A.E. Sharjah Sajaa Gas Plant Contract Worth $250 Million
-- B y   B r i a n   S w i n t
-- 2010-10-11T07:53:55Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-11/petrofac-wins-u-a-e-sharjah-sajaa-gas-plant-contract-worth-250-million.html
Petrofac Plc said it was awarded a
contract by the government of Sharjah for management of the
Sajaa Gas Plant in the United Arab Emirates. The five-year deal
is worth more than $250 million, the company said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Brian Swint at 
 bswint@bloomberg.net  